## Send Review Request

> Example Request

```shell
curl 'https://api.onvoard.com/v1/review-requesters/rw_req_awxloccld94xkfh/send' \
-H 'Authorization: Token {API_KEY}'
-d name="John Doe" \
-d email="johndoe@gmail.com"
```

> Example Response

```json
{
  "id": "rr_rcpt_3e6mz1ur0aoycy8v7jsj8aekw",
  "tracking_id": "r6kMe3QwGjE0pilgCk7Q",
