> Example Request

```shell
curl 'https://api.onvoard.com/v1/review-requesters' \
-H 'Authorization: Token {API_KEY}'
```

> Example Response

```json
{
  "num_records": 1,
  "num_pages": 1,
  "current_page": 1,
  "results": [{
    "id": "rw_req_awxloccld94xkfh",
    "name": "OnVoard G2",
    "type": "SINGLE_SITE",
